race.comment: OH TOO GOOD (5) can bounce back strongly here third up. The first up run in the G2 Lets Elope at Flemington was very good before working too hard on a strong pace at Moonee Valley, fading as a $3.70 chance. Third up last time in she was dominant in fast time and she should get every chance here from the draw. SEA WHAT I SEE (6) improved sharply to win the Gold Nugget at Ballarat second up off a poor return. Maybe wants further now but she's still lightly raced and has won 7/11. JENNILALA (2) wasn't bad in G1 company fresh and can roll across to the front here. Can give a sight. PONDALOWIE (12) is unproven at a mile but has been hitting the line well and comes through a fast race.
